{"tid":814384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同支那接軌]澳門擬設網絡安全法查核互聯網用戶身份","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:51:37.000Z","uid":51271,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e75986374f0f4b8d520360b3c15ea415bc3f4326","tid":814384,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:06:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1029512&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1029512%26csid%3D261_341&d=tYIKVQDHuTuwEEk%2FJ6p%2FTAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f3962407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1029512&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府計劃設立網絡安全法，將向立法會提交草案，建議網絡經營者向用戶提供互聯網接入服務時，須查核及登記客戶身份資料；又建議在法例生效前購買的預付電話卡，若使用者在60日內未有補交身份資料，電話卡將無法再使用。<br />\n<br />\n草案又提出，成立屬決策機關的網絡安全常設委員會；所有公共部門、運輸、電訊、銀行保險、醫療衛生、水電等共11個領域的機構，營運者有義務設立網絡安全主要負責人，在發生網絡安全事故時，須通知網絡安全事故預警及應急中心。"},{"pid":"cbb56a5d930426b5add8081dfd61f72d14e6cc53","tid":814384,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":38,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"好人好姐怕咩人查"},{"pid":"1c1db3a17ed74507d19a0e29d985fbcf202c0fd0","tid":814384,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"實名登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebad00436cf9f71fbd02f7c31c1c13961fc401a6","tid":814384,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"玄學大師末日😭"},{"pid":"4650adeb81eff32d2bd3776049322b178f937970","tid":814384,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"買電話卡實名其實冇乜野"},{"pid":"08b34c1d684acb6058e4f27671777ea0f47c9b84","tid":814384,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"